1
00:00:07,060 --> 00:00:07,900
[1983]
Wang.

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:09,920
[Jiangshun Reclamation Depot]

3
00:00:09,940 --> 00:00:10,900
I would like to confirm

4
00:00:11,060 --> 00:00:12,060
something with you.

5
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:12,740
[Wang Jiangshun, owner, fence]

6
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:13,380
I care about nothing else

7
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:15,220
as long as I get paid.

8
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:17,260
Don't you have a clue

9
00:00:17,260 --> 00:00:18,180
about why we come here?

10
00:00:18,180 --> 00:00:19,460
I totally have no idea!

11
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:21,620
What's with the yelling?

12
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:22,660
Are you out of your mind?

13
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:23,380
I'll sort things out for you.

14
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:29,460
Wang,

15
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:30,580
listen.

16
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:36,540
Ma Xiaohu

17
00:00:36,940 --> 00:00:37,940
told us something

18
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:39,740
that I wanted to verify with you.

19
00:00:40,140 --> 00:00:41,460
He was trying to frame me.

20
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:43,060
You'd be a fool if you believed him.

21
00:00:43,540 --> 00:00:45,060
I know he isn't trustworthy.

22
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:47,260
That's why I came.

23
00:00:47,460 --> 00:00:48,380
Open up.

24
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:50,620
Just ask me out there.

25
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:52,420
OK.

26
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:01,380
He said you had a secret account book.

27
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:02,780
Take it with you

28
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:04,660
and come back with us for investigation.

29
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:13,300
I knew you were coming for it.

30
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:15,020
You know what?

31
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:16,820
I've hidden it up.

32
00:01:17,540 --> 00:01:18,180
Wang,

33
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:19,820
put your gun down.

34
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:22,460
Illegal possession of firearms.

35
00:01:23,140 --> 00:01:24,100
Resisting arrest
and assaulting a policeman.

36
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:26,180
I can give an order to gun you down.

37
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:26,740
You heard him.

38
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:27,900
Put your gun down.

39
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:33,540
You two.

40
00:01:33,940 --> 00:01:34,820
Put down your guns first.

41
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:40,220
Wang,

42
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:41,620
easy.

43
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,420
We can talk things through.

44
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,300
We've known each other for years.

45
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,380
You can trust me.

46
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:48,700
I can't give you the book.

47
00:01:49,260 --> 00:01:49,860
I'm not stupid

48
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:51,140
and I don't want to die either.

49
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:53,100
Put down your gun.

50
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:54,540
We can talk about anything but not this.

51
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,020
Don't come again

52
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:57,620
and everything will be okay.

53
00:01:57,780 --> 00:01:58,260
Alright.

54
00:01:58,740 --> 00:02:00,260
You're not considering your own benefit

55
00:02:01,340 --> 00:02:01,940
but what about your son

56
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:03,500
who is working out of town?

57
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,340
Leave my son alone.

58
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:06,100
I'll kill you.

59
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:39,760
[Adapted from Zhao Junkai's novel,
Double Track Puzzle]

60
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:44,320
[Episode 20]

61
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,380
What's your plan?

62
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:10,420
We didn't see this coming.

63
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:11,580
The situation is not clear.

64
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:14,380
Sanmahu is not only your nemesis

65
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:17,020
but also a key suspect in this case.

66
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,380
Send Liu Liu and Nanyi to follow him.

67
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:21,580
Zhang and I
are leading a team to go there.

68
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:23,220
When the 766 Train
arrives at the station,

69
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,780
we'll lock down
this place for surveillance.

70
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:26,900
You can stick to your original plan

71
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,900
and act accordingly
when Sanmahu is spotted.

72
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,180
Mr. Xiong has contacted the local police

73
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,180
to block all exits.

74
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:34,380
When necessary,

75
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:36,100
the train's departure will be delayed

76
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,140
and I'll initiate
a full search of the train.

77
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,460
He'll be trapped there

78
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:40,900
the minute he sets foot
into the station.

79
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:48,480
[Train T766]

80
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:34,300
Sorry, I mistook you for someone else.

81
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:31,220
Stop right there. Don't move.

82
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:32,500
Police on duty. Move aside.

83
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:13,740
Get up.

84
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:15,620
Take him away.

85
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,260
The guy is arrested

86
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:32,180
but why aren't we leaving?

87
00:07:32,180 --> 00:07:33,460
It's already ten minutes late.

88
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:41,780
All units, attention.

89
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,140
Have you got sight of the target?

90
00:07:43,660 --> 00:07:44,620
No sight of him.

91
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:47,380
Team one, two, three.

92
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,340
Follow me. We're boarding.

93
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,460
Others, wait on the platform.

94
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:51,140
Tell the conductor

95
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,740
the train can leave in three minutes.

96
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:53,140
Got it.

97
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:34,260
Where is your boss, Mr. Sanmahu?

98
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:37,060
Sending a brat to deliver the message

99
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:38,620
and hiding in the dark?

100
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,940
Shame on him.

101
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,940
What a coward.

102
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,300
Mr. Tu,

103
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:50,220
you're not being honest.

104
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:52,860
We had a deal.

105
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:55,060
You were supposed to come alone.

106
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:57,220
See?

107
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:59,260
You can't blame Mr. Sanmahu this time,

108
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:00,020
can you?

109
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,820
What are you here for?

110
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:06,900
To check things out for Mr. Sanmahu.

111
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,940
If you keep your promise,

112
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:10,500
he'll show up.

113
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:11,860
Get it?

114
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:20,900
Stay in and lock your door.

115
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:21,740
Don't come out.

116
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:48,380
Young man,

117
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:49,900
put down your knife.

118
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:52,660
Put it down.

119
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:00,620
Attention.

120
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:03,300
Mr. Tu is having a fight on Carriage 4.

121
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:21,500
Don't move.

122
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:32,460
Jump.

123
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,300
Are you delusional?

124
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,700
You. Jump.

125
00:10:38,820 --> 00:10:39,900
Sanmahu

126
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:43,940
is at the turn coming ahead.

127
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:47,020
You won't get to see him

128
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:49,940
if you don't jump now.

129
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:54,860
Watch him

130
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,220
and tell Zhan Peng about this.

131
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,780
Mr. Zhan, Mr. Tu jumped off
to find Sanmahu.

132
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:29,940
Tell the conductor
to decelerate and stop ahead.

133
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,420
Contact Mr. Xiong right away

134
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,260
to request assistance
from the local police

135
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,860
to search the place
around the jump-off point.

136
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:37,340
We have to find Mr. Tu soon.

137
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,580
It's been 20 years.

138
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:52,060
Time for a closure.

139
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:56,780
Just cut to the chase.

140
00:11:58,540 --> 00:11:59,460
Show your weapon.

141
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,500
I haven't used one for a long time.

142
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:03,340
Later,

143
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:04,740
please forgive me for cutting you,

144
00:12:04,980 --> 00:12:06,020
shallow or deep.

145
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:19,460
Mr. Wang.

146
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:23,260
You were so freaking calm.

147
00:14:25,780 --> 00:14:26,660
Come on.

148
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,060
Uncuff me.

149
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,580
Let's go to Mr. Jiang.

150
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:33,980
I have a secret for you.

151
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:36,500
Mr. Jiang is me.

152
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,260
Why?

153
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:44,140
Because

154
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,420
I am...

155
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:47,900
Wang Jiangshun's son.

156
00:14:50,620 --> 00:14:52,300
I... I report Wang Jiangshun.

157
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:54,380
He's quite sly.

158
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,940
Last month when I went
to give him his share,

159
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:58,900
I saw that he had a secret account book

160
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:01,420
with info like amount, location,

161
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:02,300
and time in it.

162
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:12,260
I was responsible

163
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,460
for what happened.

164
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:18,340
Let things

165
00:15:19,420 --> 00:15:20,740
end...

166
00:15:20,980 --> 00:15:22,060
with me.

167
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,060
Don't hurt

168
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:25,740
any innocent people.

169
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:28,300
If you and Han Weidong

170
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:29,700
hadn't fired and caused the explosion,

171
00:15:30,740 --> 00:15:32,980
I wouldn't have lost my family.

172
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:34,540
You should all die.

173
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:36,500
All die.

174
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:41,700
You have paid

175
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:43,860
for your debt.

176
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:48,940
Now, it's Zhan's turn.

177
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:02,480
♪The night covered up
how much I missed you♪

178
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:07,760
♪The wind tried to find where you were♪

179
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:13,280
♪The flowers withered
before bearing fruit♪

180
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:18,560
♪Yet you have never left♪

181
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:24,000
♪Looking back at the once-lit fire♪

182
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:29,120
♪Didn't expect it to die down so soon♪

183
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:33,100
♪But if I ask you this♪

184
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:33,700
Mr. Tu.

185
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,460
- Mr. Tu.
- Mr. Tu.

186
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:36,220
Mr. Tu.

187
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:36,940
Call the ambulance.

188
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,260
Mr. Tu.

189
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:40,020
♪You wouldn't regret it.
We trust each other with our lives♪

190
00:16:40,020 --> 00:16:40,620
Mr. Tu.

191
00:16:40,920 --> 00:16:45,560
♪When the past finds you in your dream♪

192
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:50,560
♪And sings you an old song♪

193
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,240
[Hui]

194
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:54,040
♪When we cross
every river and mountain♪

195
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:57,480
♪To meet again♪

196
00:16:57,900 --> 00:17:00,980
♪We'll reminisce about
every second of our past♪

197
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:01,740
Keep looking.

198
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:02,900
We must find him.

199
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,420
His home. His company.

200
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:05,940
Anywhere possible.

201
00:17:13,380 --> 00:17:13,980
Han Xin.

202
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,540
Something's wrong with Wang Zhihui.

203
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:16,900
I found a bill of exchange

204
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:18,020
from an overseas account.

205
00:17:18,580 --> 00:17:20,340
It matches the record of the account book
of my dad's company.

206
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:22,300
He secretly transferred
his money to his account.

207
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:23,660
I also found an account book...

208
00:17:23,820 --> 00:17:24,780
I've already known.

209
00:17:25,060 --> 00:17:26,020
Mr. Tu is badly hurt

210
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,460
by Wang Zhihui.

211
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:28,980
Now we're searching for him
across the city.

212
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:30,900
You should protect the evidence

213
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:31,700
and stay safe.

214
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:32,980
Keep me updated.

215
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,020
OK.

216
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,720
[Xiatong Railway Hospital]

217
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,960
[Emergency Room]

218
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:53,000
[In Operation]

219
00:17:58,900 --> 00:17:59,700
Sorry,

220
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:00,620
the injury is too severe.

221
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:02,420
We have done our best

222
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:04,420
but he's in deep coma.

223
00:18:04,620 --> 00:18:06,060
He's expected to enter

224
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:08,100
a vegetative state.

225
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:10,140
The chance of the patient waking up
is very dim.

226
00:20:56,650 --> 00:20:57,920
[Han Xin:
He's at No.16 Huatengyuan Villa,]

227
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,800
[No.11 Binhe Road. Come quick.]

228
00:21:00,700 --> 00:21:01,780
We found Wang Zhihui.

229
00:21:03,140 --> 00:21:03,820
Go.

230
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:04,380
Zhang,

231
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:05,740
Nanyi, let's go.

232
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:45,420
Did you send the message?

233
00:21:46,620 --> 00:21:47,900
What are you going to do?

234
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:51,740
Where is the notebook?

235
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:53,820
I don't know.

236
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,980
My father's death

237
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:20,820
has something to do with you, right?

238
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:26,700
I'll ask you again.

239
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:31,220
Where is the notebook from my safe?

240
00:23:29,580 --> 00:23:31,540
If you don't want to tell me, fine.

241
00:23:33,500 --> 00:23:34,660
It doesn't matter.

242
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:36,000
[Sanmahu]

243
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:49,880
[Tu Hongjiang]

244
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:09,620
We both lost our fathers.

245
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:11,620
How can you smile

246
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,980
so happily?

247
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:44,740
Han Xin.

248
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:46,660
Han Xin.

249
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:54,700
Wang Zhihui, what are you going to do?

250
00:25:56,340 --> 00:25:57,220
Anyone here?

251
00:25:57,340 --> 00:25:58,340
Anyone here?

252
00:25:58,660 --> 00:25:59,580
Anyone?

253
00:26:00,420 --> 00:26:01,140
Hello?

254
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:04,380
There is

255
00:26:06,140 --> 00:26:07,380
no one.

256
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:09,860
Wang Zhihui, what's all this about?

257
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:11,500
It seems

258
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:14,140
that I underestimated you

259
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:18,220
or Han Weidong.

260
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:22,180
Now that you know who I am,

261
00:26:23,100 --> 00:26:25,100
you must have known

262
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:29,060
what Han Weidong did before.

263
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,420
My father's dead

264
00:26:35,300 --> 00:26:36,620
because of you,

265
00:26:37,380 --> 00:26:38,100
right?

266
00:26:39,340 --> 00:26:40,500
That's what he

267
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:41,740
deserved.

268
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:45,100
I was merciful enough

269
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:47,900
to allow him to commit suicide.

270
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,900
You are...

271
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,180
Mr. Jiang?

272
00:26:58,060 --> 00:26:59,260
Surprising,

273
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,460
huh?

274
00:27:01,540 --> 00:27:02,620
What do you want?

275
00:27:03,700 --> 00:27:05,460
What do I want?

276
00:27:18,980 --> 00:27:20,820
What if you're Mr. Jiang?

277
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:23,220
Worst case, we die together.

278
00:27:24,020 --> 00:27:24,820
No?

279
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,500
Who on earth are you?

280
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:01,420
My father's name

281
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:04,140
is Wang Jiangshun.

282
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:16,420
Because of you,

283
00:28:16,540 --> 00:28:20,100
he couldn't even keep his whole body.

284
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:23,260
You killed him!

285
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:27,700
I made a mistake.

286
00:28:28,300 --> 00:28:28,980
I wouldn't deny it.

287
00:28:35,980 --> 00:28:37,220
But my daughter,

288
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:41,900
she's innocent.

289
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:42,860
Innocent?

290
00:28:44,540 --> 00:28:45,700
